author: mattmann
msg: Official release of Crawler2 arch. This version of the crawler includes
numerous improvements and bug-fixes and the new design of the crawler
that is based on actions and metadata pre-conditions. The crawler is now
configurable via the Spring framework. See CHANGES.txt for a full list of
updates/improvements in this release. Thanks to all those who contributed
